{"tid":2207492,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"全民議政，加入兒童議會！！！！！！！","createTime":"2020-09-18T07:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T15:43:30.000Z","uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d06bcb251afc58461695c3aa8e8b075e05d25a6","tid":2207492,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/landscape/public/d8/images/methode/2020/09/17/c9d01dea-f8cd-11ea-a41c-8cbd1416100a_image_hires_183954.jpeg?itok=9iFh5e_O&amp;v=1600339205\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.i-scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flandscape%2Fpublic%2Fd8%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2020%2F09%2F17%2Fc9d01dea-f8cd-11ea-a41c-8cbd1416100a_image_hires_183954.jpeg%3Fitok%3D9iFh5e_O%26v%3D1600339205&h=5f968703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兒童議會 Children's Council<br />\n9月14日 11:57  &middot; <br />\n【兒童議會2020 開始接受報名｜Recruitment for Children&rsquo;s Council 2020 begins】<br />\n由 防止虐待兒童會(香港) Against Child Abuse (Hong Kong)及 香港兒童權利委員會 Hong Kong Committee on Children's Rights 合辦嘅「兒童議會2020」報名正式啟動！！！<br />\n香港兒童呢一年來面對好多唔同嘅挑戰，而我地深信兒童能夠認清自己嘅權利同責任、親身參與好重要。「兒童議會」正正係一個實踐兒童權利同理想嘅平台！<br />\n現誠邀13歲至18歲以下嘅你加入「兒童議會2020」，以兒童議員嘅身份為香港一百一十萬個兒童發聲，捍衛兒童權利！<br />\n想知更多活動詳情可以睇我地嘅網頁同留意呢個專頁。<br />\n網上報名: <a href=\"https://childrencouncil.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchildrencouncil.org.hk&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=f04e2c4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://childrencouncil.org.hk</a><br />\n查詢電話：2915 0607 / cc2020@aca.org.hk<br />\n截止日期：2020年9月28日（星期一）下午五時正（以郵戳為準）<br />\n**此計劃歡迎不同種族及有特別需要的兒童參加**<br />\n#兒童權利 #中學生  #香港 #聯合國兒童權利公約<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/55881775_1196220583867985_2795063423728091136_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=mNxL4PNhZxgAX_OERS7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=65cf67199e3c8ad7dbc84eb1252b50b6&amp;oe=5F899AD3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F55881775_1196220583867985_2795063423728091136_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DmNxL4PNhZxgAX_OERS7%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D65cf67199e3c8ad7dbc84eb1252b50b6%26oe%3D5F899AD3&h=f1e9bf98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/43207515_1084355961721115_8944120457339076608_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_sid=9267fe&amp;_nc_ohc=RyZ_l5HIBT0AX_XfsSq&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=dc50ad221b2d58f79b31ae33e493d695&amp;oe=5F89B0DD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F43207515_1084355961721115_8944120457339076608_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_sid%3D9267fe%26_nc_ohc%3DRyZ_l5HIBT0AX_XfsSq%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Ddc50ad221b2d58f79b31ae33e493d695%26oe%3D5F89B0DD&h=20d00f0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89b8eb69b341597213f6cb9d56839628d2fbb61c","tid":2207492,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">力爭35+！！！！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mb3sfXcEh5A&amp;ab_channel=childrencouncilhk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMb3sfXcEh5A%26ab_channel%3Dchildrencouncilhk&h=9f151f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們歡迎所有：<br />\n<br />\n13至18歲以下的兒童 (截至2021年1月30日)<br />\n對推動兒童權利有興趣及熱誠<br />\n具責任感，願意主動表達意見及與他人衷誠合作<br />\n參加者必須出席並積極參與所有活動<br />\n參加者是以個人名義參加，但必須有父母或監護人同意<br />\n**此計劃歡迎不同種族及有特別需要的兒童參加**<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報名辦法：<br />\n請將報名表格，連同「兒童的聲音」(中英皆可)，透過以下方法提交：<br />\n<br />\n郵寄／送交至香港新界葵涌大連排道132-134號TLP132二樓A室 「防止虐待兒童會葵涌中心」，請註明「兒童議會統籌委員會」收<br />\n傳真至：2915 0788<br />\n參加者亦可透過網上報名：<a href=\"http://www.childrencouncil.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.childrencouncil.org.hk&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=87c46949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.childrencouncil.org.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n截止日期：<br />\n2020年9月28日（星期一）下午五時正（以郵戳為準）"},{"pid":"b89749f7e66de0e8ee11ba10766bb2adc9bf4ced","tid":2207492,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T08:00:28.000Z","msg":"嘩 見你斯斯文文真係睇唔出係熱狗"},{"pid":"9a65eef05434cd4a4d1324e7db67679398d71cae","tid":2207492,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T08:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.choihung.edu.hk/Photo/378/middle/53356474186967.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.choihung.edu.hk%2FPhoto%2F378%2Fmiddle%2F53356474186967.JPG&h=b4487ba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兒童普羅政治學苑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c01e6d64cc3e0e1f58f036a831c889bac6f6fd3","tid":2207492,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"左起：N賓、大雞樂、貓貓禮志、M_Lanzini<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20841856_834981929991854_2986610756175544536_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=I5F8uJBBykEAX8H3yv3&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=c6a15e45590acab135bc97f6b7b33e9a&amp;oe=5F881B1A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20841856_834981929991854_2986610756175544536_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DI5F8uJBBykEAX8H3yv3%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Dc6a15e45590acab135bc97f6b7b33e9a%26oe%3D5F881B1A&h=405c925e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99abba1a20d284f1cf1ca7e54c7f2a277607d72f","tid":2207492,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T08:05